## 核心模型

### `MOD-ADP-033` live all-arXiv dry-run

- status: active
- purpose: 在 GitHub/cloud runner 上验证全 arXiv 主档案桶扫描，不依赖本机 Mac 后台。
- inputs: arXiv primary archive buckets, max_results_per_category, generated_at, polite delay.
- outputs: dry-run report, sample daily input, scan plan, candidate count, archive coverage.
- key_parameters: `ADP_ARXIV_MAX_RESULTS_PER_CATEGORY=3` fallback for scheduled/trial-start workflows.
- code_refs: `arxiv-daily-push/src/arxiv_daily_push/global_scan.py`; `.github/workflows/arxiv-daily-push-phase12-cloud-dry-run.yml`
- test_refs: `arxiv-daily-push/tests/test_global_scan.py`; `arxiv-daily-push/tests/test_cloud_dry_run_workflow.py`
- evidence_refs: `github-actions://LinzeColin/CodexProject/actions/runs/28019921500/artifacts/7818287996`
- fallback_behavior: Fail closed on blocked archive, insufficient candidate count, or side-effect mismatch.

### `MOD-ADP-045` accelerated Stage 1 acceptance

- status: active
- purpose: 从通过的 GitHub/cloud live all-arXiv dry-run、至少 30 个真实候选和受控 Gmail SMTP refs 生成 Stage 1 acceptance 证据。
- inputs: live dry-run JSON, controlled SMTP manifest, expected_samples=30.
- outputs: acceptance report with `ARXIV_PRODUCTION_ACCEPTED` only when all gates pass.
- assumptions: no new real email send, no video generation, no GitHub Release requirement, production schedule disabled.
- formula_refs: `FORM-ADP-047`
- parameter_refs: `PARAM-ADP-349`, `PARAM-ADP-350`, `PARAM-ADP-351`
- code_refs: `arxiv-daily-push/src/arxiv_daily_push/stage1_accelerated_acceptance.py`
- test_refs: `arxiv-daily-push/tests/test_stage1_accelerated_acceptance.py`
- evidence_refs: `governance/run_manifests/ADP-S1P5T04-ARXIV-PRODUCTION-ACCEPTED-20260623.json`
- fallback_behavior: If candidate count, SMTP refs, artifact status, or side-effect policy fails, output `BLOCKED` and do not claim acceptance.

### `MOD-ADP-046` real arXiv 30 as-of replay

- status: active
- purpose: 用真实 arXiv Atom submittedDate date-window 补跑 30 个历史 as-of date，生成 daily input、B1 teaching report、中文 email preview、queue ledger 和 CONTENT_LEDGER rows。
- inputs: generated_at, start_date, end_date, count=30, lookback_days=7, max_results=10, recipient, artifact_dir, fetcher.
- outputs: replay report, `daily_inputs.jsonl`, `reports.md`, `email_previews.txt`, `queue_ledgers.jsonl`, `run_records.jsonl`, `CONTENT_LEDGER.csv`.
- assumptions: no SMTP send, no Release upload, no video generation, no scheduler enablement, no secret values.
- formula_refs: `FORM-ADP-048`
- parameter_refs: `PARAM-ADP-352`..`PARAM-ADP-359`
- code_refs: `arxiv-daily-push/src/arxiv_daily_push/stage1_real_replay.py`
- test_refs: `arxiv-daily-push/tests/test_stage1_real_replay.py`
- evidence_refs: `governance/run_manifests/ADP-S1P5T03-REAL-ARXIV-30-ASOF-REPLAY-20260623.json`
- fallback_behavior: If any date fails, candidate selection is missing, future leakage appears, duplicate lead appears, queue continuity breaks, P0/P1 unsupported claims appear, or production side effects are true, output `BLOCKED`.

